snippet.title: TRIGGER WARNING: AUDIO of Amber Portwood coming after Andrew Glennon and son with machete.
snippet.description:
New audio clips released detail the moment that Amber Portwood went after Andrew Glennon with a machete while he was holding their child.  Shocking audio clips, and surveillance footage ahead, so please be warned of anyone who finds this subject matter to be triggering.  

Stay until the end for how to enter our biggest giveaway!  Teen Mom fans make sure to enter, you won't want to miss this!  

SUBSCRIBE to our channel, hit the notification bell, and join the conversation down in the comments!
